                <head>No. 80.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to General <persName
                            type="to">Schenck</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1872-06-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 1, 1872</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The fifth Article of the Treaty requires the written arguments to be presented by
                    the 15th Jane.</p>
                <p>The adjournment of the Tribunal without amending that Article would, as we are
                    advised, practically amount to a discontinuance, and that Article can be amended
                    only by a new treaty.</p>
                <p>The opinion attributed to me regarding the Senate Article is very incorrectly
                    represented.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
